OL,3,CConcerns about treatment of staff at
OL,4,CBelfast Trust raised in 2023
OL,6,FUTV can reveal that concerns about
OL,7,Fstaff being treated poorly at the
OL,8,FBelfast Trust were raised to
OL,9,Fmanagement back in 2023 - two years
OL,10,Fbefore the recent cardiac surgery unit
OL,11,Fscandal.
OL,13,FOne of the issues that was raised at
OL,14,Fthe time was an alleged culture of
OL,15,Ffear where staff felt that would be
OL,16,Fpunished for speaking out.
