OL,3,CConcerns about treatment of staff at
OL,4,CBelfast Trust raised in 2023
OL,6,FThere were also reports of alleged
OL,7,Fbullying, controlling behaviour, as
OL,8,Fwell as a data-driven environment that
OL,9,Ffelt intrusive and without a clear
OL,10,Fpurpose.
OL,12,FDUP MLA Diane Dodds said: "I do not
OL,13,Funderstand how any organisation thinks
OL,14,Fit could actually develop and do
OL,15,Freally important work that it is
OL,16,Fsupposed to do in this particular
OL,17,Fatmosphere."
