OL,3,CConcerns about treatment of staff at
OL,4,CBelfast Trust raised in 2023
OL,6,FThe same expert who authored the 2023
OL,7,Fbriefing is now advising the Health
OL,8,FMinister on culture and behaviour in
OL,9,Fthe wake of the cardiac surgery unit
OL,10,Fscandal.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Belfast Trust said
OL,13,Fit has been working to "create a more
OL,14,Fopen, just, and learning culture"
OL,15,Fsince 2021.
OL,17,FIt added: "This has included engaging
OL,18,Fwith experts in psychological safety
OL,19,Fto help develop resources for managers
OL,20,Fand staff, and to improve culture and
OL,21,Fbehaviours within teams.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
