OL,3,CConcerns about treatment of staff at
OL,4,CBelfast Trust raised in 2023
OL,6,F"There is still work to be done, and
OL,7,Fnumerous cultural programmes of work
OL,8,Fare underway.
OL,10,F"The Trust has begun a campaign to
OL,11,Fencourage and support staff to speak
OL,12,Fup, in response to the cardiac surgery
OL,13,Freview.
OL,15,F"This includes a commitment to support
OL,16,Fstaff across the Trust to speak up
OL,17,Fthrough various means. Staff have also
OL,18,Fbeen signposted to the Trust
OL,19,Fwhistleblowing process, which has been
OL,20,Fdeveloped considerably over the last
OL,21,Ffew years."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
