OL,3,CConcerns about treatment of staff at
OL,4,CBelfast Trust raised in 2023
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Department of Health
OL,7,Fsaid: "Peter McBride made a
OL,8,Fpresentation in 2023 to the Belfast
OL,9,FHSC Trust Board in relation to
OL,10,Forganisational culture. This reflected
OL,11,Fthe responsibilities of the Trust
OL,12,FBoard for staff welfare.
OL,14,F"The department has been providing
OL,15,Foversight and support to the Trust
OL,16,Fthrough its Support and Intervention
OL,17,FFramework (SIF). This has included the
OL,18,Fformal commissioning ` with the Public
OL,19,FHealth Agency ` of the independent
OL,20,Freview of the cardiac surgical unit.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
