OL,3,CConcerns about treatment of staff at
OL,4,CBelfast Trust raised in 2023
OL,6,F"The oversight of the Trust has been
OL,7,Fescalated to Level 5 ` a step taken in
OL,8,Fonly the most serious and exceptional
OL,9,Fcases.
OL,11,F"Reviewing whistleblowing processes
OL,12,Fwill be an important part of the Level
OL,13,F5 intervention. The Minister has
OL,14,Fpublicly made clear that he wants
OL,15,Fassurance that any HSC employee with
OL,16,Fconcerns about bullying or other
OL,17,Funacceptable behaviours is properly
OL,18,Flistened to and supported."
